345
00:21:09,324 --> 00:21:12,043
What a delight. How nice to meet you.
l was just talking about your stuff.

346
00:21:12,124 --> 00:21:14,513
l was... They call me the artist.

347
00:21:14,604 --> 00:21:15,957
(LAUGHlNG)

348
00:21:16,564 --> 00:21:18,475
-How dare they?
-Yeah, yeah.

349
00:21:18,564 --> 00:21:22,273
-So this is your stuff. That's extraordinary.
-This is all my scarecrows.

350
00:21:22,364 --> 00:21:24,480
-And l have 90.
-Ninety?

351
00:21:24,564 --> 00:21:26,236
Ninety scarecrows, yes.

352
00:21:26,324 --> 00:21:30,681
And l dress them all new every year.
l've been doing that since the last 13 years.

353
00:21:30,764 --> 00:21:34,040
-There's something wrong with you.
