355
00:21:37,204 --> 00:21:38,842
lt's a big job.

356
00:21:38,924 --> 00:21:41,996
lt is very unusual.

357
00:21:42,284 --> 00:21:45,162
l try to put, see, a little note
on each one of them.

358
00:21:45,244 --> 00:21:49,203
Like, even that guy that l call Wayne.
Like, he died two years ago.

359
00:21:49,284 --> 00:21:52,082
But he was a miner.
He worked hard all his life.

360
00:21:52,164 --> 00:21:55,998
So that's why l put ''Wayne Collins''
on the scarecrow.

361
00:21:56,084 --> 00:22:00,043
-Yeah, so now that's a memorial to him.
