00:23:12,044 --> 00:23:13,682
There's no mistake he plays well.

376
00:23:13,764 --> 00:23:16,198
You know, his art is good. His life is good.

377
00:23:16,284 --> 00:23:18,195
He's a true, nice man.

378
00:23:19,644 --> 00:23:21,123
What a jolly day!

379
00:23:21,804 --> 00:23:22,919
You crazy people.

380
00:23:23,564 --> 00:23:25,919
You are. You're French.
That's what's wrong with you.

381
00:23:32,764 --> 00:23:34,880
BlLLY: I like this bit of the world. It's happy.

