00:23:34,964 --> 00:23:37,797
There's a continental happiness
that really appeals to me.

383
00:23:40,764 --> 00:23:42,880
Even the landscape lifts your spirit.

384
00:23:45,364 --> 00:23:48,322
Just north of Cheticamp is
the scenic Cabot Trail,

385
00:23:48,404 --> 00:23:50,838
named after the early explorer John Cabot.

386
00:23:51,364 --> 00:23:55,152
