of the top five motorcycle rides in the world.

390
00:24:09,324 --> 00:24:12,555
I can understand why. It's spectacular.

391
00:24:26,124 --> 00:24:28,354
What a stunning place.

392
00:24:28,444 --> 00:24:30,321
My God, it's beautiful.

393
00:24:34,724 --> 00:24:37,921
lt's a lovely feeling rolling along
in the open air,

394
00:24:38,004 --> 00:24:40,564
especially when you get
to the top of these hills

