Look at that. Pleasant Bay.

403
00:25:14,884 --> 00:25:17,557
Strange little name,
but it kind of sums it up, really.

404
00:25:17,644 --> 00:25:20,602
This is at the very end of Nova Scotia,
Cape Breton,

405
00:25:20,684 --> 00:25:23,562
New Brunswick,
all that Acadian stuff we showed you.

406
00:25:23,644 --> 00:25:25,714
This is up towards the end of it.

