00:27:14,964 --> 00:27:17,273
and it's a thing that appealed to me as a boy.

436
00:27:17,364 --> 00:27:20,879
lt always smelled of foreign places

437
00:27:20,964 --> 00:27:24,115
and leaving and going on a voyage
and being a man

438
00:27:24,204 --> 00:27:27,082
and growing up and all that kind of thing.

